problem_text_cn: 如图,已知⊙O的半径为5,弦AB,CD所对的圆心角分别是∠AOB,∠COD,若∠AOB与∠COD互补,弦AB=8,则弦CD的长为()
problem_text_en: As shown in the figure, it is known that the radius of ⊙O is N_0, and the central angles of chord AB and CD are ∠AOB and ∠COD respectively. If ∠AOB and ∠COD are complementary, chord AB = N_1, then the length of chord CD is ()
raw_answer: 解:如图,延长AO交⊙O于点E,连接BE,则∠AOB+∠BOE=180°,又∵∠AOB+∠COD=180°,∴∠BOE=∠COD,∴BE=CD,∵AE为⊙O的直径,∴∠ABE=90°,∴CD=√{AE^{2}-AB^{2}}=√{10^{2}-8^{2}}=6,故选:A．
